{
  "stem": "7683.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he is the son of the family, and I think he should have it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we gave the-- him, that he has the hotel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started a textile business with a partner, what was our own thing to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was not the right-- probably I should have listened to Selma.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had said this is not the right person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, so he had the location.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had-- I could get from her family's family-- her family-- from her family-- also a license.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in Holland, whatever you do, you need a special license for it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if-- you cannot just start a business just like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have a special license.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I could get this kind of a license to start the business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came out on the hotel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and he had the location.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we figure we can make one thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for years, it was fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We did make very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I loved it in Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved it in Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- well, for me it wasn't not that I left that all my family is killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't have any feeling that I have anti-Semites in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- so for me, life was now-- and then, we-- there was something in the business didn't go right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- I also-- I have to leave the business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was starting other business-- I was not so successful with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I decided-- and I wanted-- I said let's go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wanted to go to America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you couldn't get-- the quota was very minimal for Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we could go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
